{"tid":695523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人階級計分表","createTime":"2018-06-09T09:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T11:42:30.000Z","uid":86246,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"440d70765ed1ca6e3d812377f5ef8085a870dc3c","tid":695523,"uid":86246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:16:14.000Z","msg":"未來10年香港應該跟哂物業資產出身分等級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPart 1: 物業<br />\n1. 山頂<br />\n2. 傳統豪宅 eg 九龍塘 半山 九肚山 京士柏 淺水灣 etc<br />\n3. 新晉豪宅 eg 凱旋門 君臨天下 etc<br />\n4. 偽豪宅<br />\n5. 市區私樓 (有會所)<br />\n6. 新市鎮私樓 (有會所)  eg 將軍澳 馬鞍山<br />\n7. 元屯天私樓 (有會所)<br />\n8. 單棟舊私樓<br />\n9. 居屋<br />\n10. 公屋 (已買)<br />\n11. 租樓 <br />\n12. 租公屋<br />\n13. 租剮房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def579427cc2029b01d0dd5977336e05372cf683","tid":695523,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:17:08.000Z","msg":"外國物業呢"},{"pid":"ca0482043274b0c6f1527f83f7488a98f156b76c","tid":695523,"uid":86246,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"Part 2: 職業/出身<br />\n<br />\n1. 大家族後代<br />\n2. 上市公司主席後代<br />\n3. 普通屋企生意<br />\n4. 新晉startup 老闆 (成功個類 廢野唔計)<br />\n5. 雞<br />\n6. 傳統專業人士 eg AO 醫生 律師<br />\n7. 次級專業人士 eg 會計師 工程師<br />\n8.半專業人士 eg 高層it 測量師<br />\n9. 銀行/金融<br />\n10. 普通打工仔 &lt;30k<br />\n11. 體力勞動人士 <br />\n12. 綜援<br />\n13. 普通打工仔 &lt;20k"},{"pid":"d931495402f03c88f48a36d344ce9715d6ec82dd","tid":695523,"uid":134012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"租山頂點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc56e5e4c5e14c5a733b4933256d4204ead26411"